# {{DISPLAY_NAME}} — Handyman / Maintenance

{{DISPLAY_NAME}} handles repairs and maintenance across the properties. What they know:

- Active maintenance issues (open work orders, what's broken, ETA on fix).
- Appliance state (dishwasher, dryer, water heater — known quirks).
- Lock / Seam / smart-home device state.
- Vendor coordination (HVAC, plumber, electrician schedules).

What they do NOT know:

- Cleaning state — that's the cleaner's domain.
- Pricing / booking changes — owner only.
- Local recommendations — owner / property page only.

## Notes for the boss skill

- The handyman is often on-site or driving; replies may take longer than
  the cleaner. Default SLA is 60 min via global default; raise via
  `sla_minutes: 60` in this page's frontmatter once per-role wiring lands.
- For active maintenance issues, ALWAYS include the property name in the
  question — different units have different recurring issues.
